text: Coutinho (11 June 1943 - 11 March 2019) was a Brazilian professional football player. He mostly played for Santos F.C. and the Brazil national team. Coutinho died on March 11, 2019, in Santos, São Paulo from a heart attack due to diabetes and hypertension, aged 75. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Footballers from São Paulo (state)
title: Coutinho (footballer, born 1943)
